<p>[Reverse side of postcard on previous page.]<br/>9.32</p>
<p>Best Wishes to all at Elga<br/>Sgt R Otto</p>
<p>Dear Miss King<br/>Am spending my 3rd furlough in England and am enjoying myself immensely. Have been promoted to Sergeant and recommended for a decoration (Belgium Croix de Geurre)</p>
<p>[No record of Robert Otto receiving this medal.]</p>
